tags.name:
lrn-table
`Accessibly render a HTML table from a csv file`
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `lrn-table`
 * @customElement lrn-table
 * `Accessibly render a HTML table from a csv file`
 *
 * @microcopy - language worth noting:
 *  - CSV - Comma separated values
 *

 * @polymer
 * @polymerLegacy
 * @demo demo/index.html
 */

attributes.name: title
attributes.description: Title of this table. This is both for accessibility and presentation.

attributes.name: csv-file
attributes.description: The file to load material from.

attributes.name: description
attributes.description: An extended description of the material in the table for improved accessibility.

properties.name: title
properties.description: Title of this table. This is both for accessibility and presentation.

properties.name: csvFile
properties.description: The file to load material from.

properties.name: description
properties.description: An extended description of the material in the table for improved accessibility.
